https://certbot.eff.org/lets-encrypt/ubuntuxenial-nginx

- Install Certbot for Nginx through apt in Ubuntu 16.04

    $ sudo apt update
    $ sudo apt install software-properties-common
    # adding the certbot ppa
    $ sudo add-apt-repository ppa:certbot/certbot
    $ sudo apt update
    $ sudo apt install python-certbot-nginx

- Get a certificate and have Cerbot edit the nginx configuration automatically 

    $ sudo certbot --nginx

- Same thing but manual nginx config  editing

    $ sudo certbot certonly --nginx

- Testing automatic renewal

    sudo certbot renew --dry-run

- Install with pip3 (make sure you have uninstalled and purged the apt version)

    sudo apt uninstall certbot
    sudo apt purge certbot
    sudo pip3 install certbot
    sudo pip3 install certbot-nginx
